{{- /*
  D-17-04 WP-17-04-05.5 — replaces plane-credentials.env.tmpl after the
  Plane CE → OpenProject substrate flip. We read `token` (the iap-sync
  user's API token, minted by scripts/openproject-mint-iap-sync-token.sh).
  Read-only consumer per ADR-A-006: xindex never writes to OpenProject.
*/ -}}
